{"type":"message","id":"cbf1b5f8","parentId":"65ca91bc","timestamp":"2026-03-30T14:06:12.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_OANjhF9iK7dOELGl48e1mNzH|fc_07b64bc35dd48fb50169ca834fcf7c8193a11844f074a4926b","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\README.md","oldText":"## Quick validation\nExpected behavior:\n- valid subagent registration with `childSessionKey` -> succeeds and is written to `active_tasks.json`\n- invalid subagent registration without `childSessionKey` -> fails immediately with a clear error\n","newText":"## Quick validation\nExpected behavior:\n- valid subagent registration with `childSessionKey` -> succeeds and is written to `active_tasks.json`\n- invalid subagent registration without `childSessionKey` -> fails immediately with a clear error\n\n## Configurable thresholds\nDefined in `config.json`:\n- `stallMinutes` — minutes without runtime evidence before a task becomes `stalled`\n- `orphanMinutes` — minutes without runtime evidence before a task becomes `orphaned`\n\n## Manual audit check\nRun:\n`python .\\\\task_watchdog\\\\check_watchdog.py`\n\nReturns a compact JSON summary with:\n- total active tasks\n- counts by status\n- flagged tasks (`stalled`, `orphaned`, `failed`)\n- current threshold config\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\task_watchdog\\\\README.md\",\"oldText\":\"## Quick validation\\nExpected behavior:\\n- valid subagent registration with `childSessionKey` -> succeeds and is written to `active_tasks.json`\\n- invalid subagent registration without `childSessionKey` -> fails immediately with a clear error\\n\",\"newText\":\"## Quick validation\\nExpected behavior:\\n- valid subagent registration with `childSessionKey` -> succeeds and is written to `active_tasks.json`\\n- invalid subagent registration without `childSessionKey` -> fails immediately with a clear error\\n\\n## Configurable thresholds\\nDefined in `config.json`:\\n- `stallMinutes` — minutes without runtime evidence before a task becomes `stalled`\\n- `orphanMinutes` — minutes without runtime evidence before a task becomes `orphaned`\\n\\n## Manual audit check\\nRun:\\n`python .\\\\\\\\task_watchdog\\\\\\\\check_watchdog.py`\\n\\nReturns a compact JSON summary with:\\n- total active tasks\\n- counts by status\\n- flagged tasks (`stalled`, `orphaned`, `failed`)\\n- current threshold config\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":176,"output":262,"cacheRead":54272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54710,"cost":{"input":0.00044,"output":0.00393,"cacheRead":0.013568,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.017938000000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774879565640,"responseId":"resp_07b64bc35dd48fb50169ca834e760881939aaf07878e5f38f7"}}
